    <item>
      <title>拉加德称欧洲央行需要时间来权衡通胀不确定性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/lagarde-says-ecb-will-need-time-to-weigh-inflation-uncertainties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，目前还没有足够的证据表明通胀威胁已经过去——这加剧了人们对央行本月将暂停降息的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/lagarde-says-ecb-will-need-time-to-weigh-inflation-uncertainties</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BREIT 免除提款限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-01/breit-waives-withdrawal-limit-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黑石集团 570 亿美元的房地产信托允许投资者提取他们要求的所有现金，即使在赎回额突破关键门槛之后也是如此。彭博社的 John Gittelsohn 报道了这一消息。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-01/breit-waives-withdrawal-limit-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 18:41:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前亿万富翁因诈骗高盛、谷歌投资者被判处七年半监禁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/ex-billionaire-gets-7-1-2-year-sentence-for-defrauding-investors-goldman-google</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位曾周游世界的芝加哥亿万富翁因在一家广告初创公司诈骗 10 亿美元而被判处七年半监禁，该公司的投资者包括高盛集团、谷歌母公司 Alphabet Inc. 和伊利诺伊州州长 JB Pritzker 的风险投资公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/ex-billionaire-gets-7-1-2-year-sentence-for-defrauding-investors-goldman-google</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 18:41:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
