    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克将偿还 2.2 亿美元债务以结束“金枪鱼债券”风波</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/mozambique-to-pay-220-million-debt-to-end-tuna-bond-saga</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克同意向 VTB Capital Plc 和葡萄牙商业银行 (Banco Comercial Português S.A.) 等债权人支付 2.2 亿美元，作为该国长达十年的金枪鱼债券丑闻的一部分，该丑闻最终以债务违约告终。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/mozambique-to-pay-220-million-debt-to-end-tuna-bond-saga</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 18:30:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院裁决显示美元仍有上涨空间，美元获得额外提振</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/dollar-gets-extra-boost-as-supreme-court-ruling-signals-currency-has-room-to-run</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最高法院一项重要裁决之后，美元上涨，凸显出如果唐纳德·特朗普再次出任总统，美元还有进一步上涨的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/dollar-gets-extra-boost-as-supreme-court-ruling-signals-currency-has-room-to-run</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 18:26:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着美国中部天气转冷，美国天然气价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/us-natural-gas-declines-as-weather-moves-cooler-in-central-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于天气预报显示美国中部地区天气转冷，美国天然气期货价格下跌。天然气库存仍远高于五年平均水平，引发市场供应过剩的担忧，而产量强劲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/us-natural-gas-declines-as-weather-moves-cooler-in-central-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 14:24:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
